quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  20,13,"Miin mi Suɓike ma Jento ko wonaa Wahyineede ko."
  20,14,"Pellet, ko miinn Woni Alla deweteeɗo alaa si wonaa miin n rewam; ñiiɓi e Juulde nde fii Annditugol am."
  20,15,"Pellet, Darnga ko aroowa Miɗo ɗeɓa suuɗude ngo fii yoɓe kala woŋkii ko ki gollu no."
  20,16,"Wota faddo ma e gaayi maggal on mo gooŋ- ɗinaani ngo o jokki mbeleeɗe makko o halkii."
  20,17,"Ko holɗuum woni ka ñaamo maaɗa an Muusaa?"
  20,18,"O maaki: "Ndu ko tuggordu am miɗo tuggoo ndu miɗo liwtirana ndu dammi am ɗin, miɗo mari kadi haajuuji gɗɗi e mayru"."
  20,19,"O Daali: "weddo ndu, aan Muusaa"."
  20,20,"O weddi ndu, tawi kayru ko ndu mbooɗdi won'ndi e yahde."
  20,21,"O Daali: "Nanngu ndi wota a hul min ngartira ndu e mba'adi mayru araniri ndi"."
  20,22,"Naatnu junngo maaɗa ngo ka ndeer seŋgo maa; ngo yalta ko ngo raneewo ko aldaa e rafi ɗum ko Aaya goo."
  20,23,"Fii yo min n kollle immorde e aayeeje amen aawɗe ɗe."
  20,24,"Yah to Fir'awna, pellet, kaŋko o bewi."
  20,25,"O maaki: "Jooma Yaacnanam ɓernde am nde."
  20,26,"Newinana am fiyaake am on."
  20,27,"Piɓtaa fiɓnde nde e ɗemngal am."
  20,28,"Fii yoo ɓe pahmu konngol am ngol."
  20,29,"Mbaɗanaa kam ballo jeyaaɗo ka ɓeynguure am."
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musiɗɗo am o."
  20,31,"Semmbinir mo darnde am."
  20,32,"Tawnaa mo e ndeer fiyaake am o."
  20,33,"Fii yo mon cenine ko herwi."
  20,34,"Min jaŋtomaa ko heewi."
  20,35,"Pellet, aan a wonii kumpitiiɗo min ."
  20,36,"O Daali: "Gooŋɗii a okkaama toraare maaɗa nde aan Muusaa"."
  20,37,"Gooŋɗii n neeminiino ma e laawol goɗngol."